videos.headline: Oklahoma State strikes first with 23-yard TD pass
videos.description: Taylor Cornelius fights to avoids a sack and finds J.D. King wide open for a 23-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Vasher hauls in 12-yard touchdown for Texas Tech
videos.description: Alan Bowman connects with T.J. Vasher for a 12-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Cowboys reclaim lead with 13-yard rushing TD
videos.description: Justice Hill runs up the middle for a 13-yard Oklahoma State touchdown.

videos.headline: Felton runs in untouched for a 17-yard touchdown.
videos.description: The Red Raiders increase their lead on the Cowboys as Demarcus Felton rushes in from 17-yards out.
